{"id":1640955,"retrievedAt":"2026-02-24T12:00:08.096Z","response":{"adult":false,"backdrop_path":null,"belongs_to_collection":null,"budget":0,"genres":[],"homepage":"","id":1640955,"imdb_id":null,"origin_country":["US"],"original_language":"en","original_title":"Two Worlds - One Planet","overview":"The incidence of Asperger syndrome and other forms of autism in the United States appear to be increasing dramatically. This powerful, eye-opening documentary brings the issue out of the shadows, stressing that young people with these developmental disabilities can learn and grow, if their individual needs, styles, and abilities are respected. Two Worlds — One Planet takes an upbeat look at students attending Gateway Academy, a private K-12 day school specializing in youth with Asperger Syndrome, high-functioning Autism and Pervasive Developmental Disorder. The film offers a rare opportunity to enter the world of children with Asperger's and Autism, and to see it through their own eyes and the eyes of their families. Their parents show remarkable and sometimes painful candor in revealing autism's impact on the entire family.","popularity":0.0143,"poster_path":null,"production_companies":[],"production_countries":[],"release_date":"2008-01-01","revenue":0,"runtime":62,"spoken_languages":[],"status":"Released","tagline":"","title":"Two Worlds - One Planet","video":false,"vote_average":0,"vote_count":0,"alternative_titles":{"titles":[]},"credits":{"cast":[],"crew":[{"adult":false,"gender":1,"id":2108512,"known_for_department":"Directing","name":"Gail Levin","original_name":"Gail Levin","popularity":1.1966,"profile_path":null,"credit_id":"699c59d8673f5a08f9e8f997","department":"Directing","job":"Director"},{"adult":false,"gender":1,"id":80928,"known_for_department":"Acting","name":"Ann Reinking","original_name":"Ann Reinking","popularity":0.3275,"profile_path":"/sFZqoa0A1Ge8jVnDQhUs5jWgjAE.jpg","credit_id":"699c5c920018171c160e5864","department":"Production","job":"Producer"}